-/**
- * iova_bitmap_set() - Records an IOVA range in bitmap
- * @bitmap: IOVA bitmap
- * @iova: IOVA to start
- * @length: IOVA range length
- *
- * Set the bits corresponding to the range [iova .. iova+length-1] in
